title: #103 - Chris D'Elia
description: On this episode The H3 Podcast we are joined once again by standup comedian/podcaster Chris D'Elia. Together we discuss offensive movies about midgets, Eminem impressions, bad Mathew McConaughey commercials, thicc otters, pop n' lockin for Jesus, and R. Kelly songs about getting your vaccinations!
